import TextRow from '@/case_study/reusable/TextRow.astro';
---
<div class="cards1 flex flex-col">
    <TextRow title="Design Highlights" >
      <p>Our UX team worked in sprints using the Design Thinking framework. After mapping clinic workflows, we designed interfaces for every user type: radiologists, technicians, admins, and reception staff.</p>
      <h3>Key UX Wins:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Realtime dashboards for patients, queues, and scans</li>
        <li>Color-coded patient states and quick actions</li>
        <li>Role-based UIs for staff (Doctor, Admin, Receptionist)</li>
        <li>Dark/light mode and low-bandwidth optimization</li>
        <li>Mobile-friendly design for clinic staff on the go</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We focused on clarity, hierarchy, and speed â€” interfaces that reduce clicks, minimize errors, and work in low-connectivity clinics.</p>
    </TextRow>

</div>




